    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence. Pressure-head and hemolysis-index validation results demonstrate adequate model agreement. The velocity-field validation result notes that aleatory uncertainty from inter-experiment variability was assessed qualitatively by the test team; while this qualitative assessment supports confidence in the result, no structured uncertainty quantification node was linked to that result record. The overall credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the Accepted decision for the CPB use COU.",
